' description: issue-tracker agent 写路径 sequence — report_issue / append_issue_context / GC + event→UI
' last_updated: 2026-05-30
@startuml issue-tracker-flow

title issue-tracker — agent 写路径 sequence (report / append source-bound / GC scheduler + event→UI)

' agent 只写不查 (仅 report_issue + append_issue_context 两 write tool); UI 读改删走 IPC (见架构图)
' 详细 module / 函数名 / commit / REVIEW 见 INDEX 第 3 列

actor "Agent\n(SDK session)" as A
participant "report_issue /\nappend_issue_context\n(mcp write tool)" as Tool
participant "issue 持久层\n(issue-repo)" as Repo
database "SQLite\n(issues + issue_appendices)" as DB
participant "事件总线\n(eventBus)" as Bus
participant "渲染层\n(issues-store → Issues UI)" as UI
participant "GC 调度器\n(IssueLifecycleScheduler 6h tick)" as GC

== report_issue: 上报新 issue ==

A -> Tool: report_issue(title, description, kind?, severity?, repro?, labels?, cwd?, logsRef?)
note right of Tool
  sourceSessionId 闭包注入 = callerSessionId (§不变量 3)
  cwd fallback: args.cwd > session.cwd > null
  kind default 'follow-up' (软枚举) / severity default 'medium'
  deny external caller (写 issues 表 + closure sid)
end note
Tool -> Repo: create({...})
Repo -> DB: INSERT issues (status='open', deleted_at=null)
Repo --> Tool: IssueRecord (主键字段 id)
Tool -> Bus: emit issue-changed { kind:'created', issue, sourceSessionId }
Tool --> A: ok(IssueRecord) — 含 id 给后续 append 当入参 issueId 用
Bus -> UI: IPC issue-changed → store upsert → 列表/详情实时刷新

== append_issue_context: 同 session 追加现场 (source-bound) ==

A -> Tool: append_issue_context(issueId, additionalContext, logsRef?)
Tool -> Repo: get(issueId)
note right of Tool
  4 道守门 (详 issue-tracker-append-decision 决策图):
  not-found / source-bound / resolved / 软删 → reject
end note
Tool -> Repo: appendContext({ issueId, body, logsRef })
Repo -> DB: INSERT issue_appendices (不动 issues.description §不变量 9)
note right of Repo
  logsRef merge (§D17): date 覆盖 / tsRange min-max 扩展
  / scopes union 去重 / note 追加截断
end note
Repo --> Tool: IssueRecord (含 appendices 子列表 §D19)
Tool -> Bus: emit issue-changed { kind:'appended', issue }
Tool --> A: ok(IssueRecord + appendices)
Bus -> UI: IPC issue-changed → store 更新

== GC: 周期硬删超期 issue (软删 / resolved 双轨) ==

GC -> Repo: listForGc({ resolvedRetentionDays, softDeletedRetentionDays })
note right of GC
  6h tick (默认); 阈值=0 跳过该轨
  resolved && resolved_at < now-N天  OR  deleted_at < now-M天
end note
Repo --> GC: { resolvedExpired[], softDeletedExpired[] }
loop 逐条 (per-id try/catch 不整批崩)
  GC -> Repo: get(id) snapshot (删前拿 sourceSessionId)
  GC -> Repo: hardDelete(id)
  Repo -> DB: DELETE issues (issue_appendices ON DELETE CASCADE 级联删)
  GC -> Bus: emit issue-changed { kind:'hardDeleted', issue:null, sourceSessionId }
end
Bus -> UI: IPC issue-changed → store 移除

@enduml
